messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Find whoever I contacted last, change his cell to +10293847563.

I’m not able to see who you most recently contacted—our address book only stores the contact entries themselves, not your call or message history. Could you tell me the name (or any other detail) of the person whose number you’d like changed to +102 938 47563?
Sorry, I don't have any more information about that person.

I’m afraid I can’t tell which entry corresponds to the person you contacted most recently unless we know something about the contact—name, current number, relationship, anything unique.  

If you’re not sure, I can list all the contacts in your address book so you can pick the one you meant. Would you like me to do that?
Sure, feel free to go ahead.
